WEBVTT

00:03:29.029 --> 00:03:30.809
kalsiy karbonatning shakllanishi

00:03:30.809 --> 00:03:33.259
uchun ideal sharoit yaratadi.

00:03:33.259 --> 00:03:35.329
Bu kristallar asta-sekin 
bo'shliqlarni

00:03:35.329 --> 00:03:36.839
to'ldirib, taxminan uch haftada

00:03:36.839 --> 00:03:38.219
mehnatsevar mikroblar

00:03:38.219 --> 00:03:39.919
deyarli 1mm kenglikdagi

00:03:39.919 --> 00:03:42.699
yoriqlarni to'liq tuzata oladi.

00:03:42.699 --> 00:03:43.869
Yoriqlarni yamagach,

00:03:43.869 --> 00:03:46.049
bakteriya va zamburug'lar
spora hosil qilib,

00:03:46.049 --> 00:03:47.569
yangi yoriqlar paydo bo'lganida

00:03:47.569 --> 00:03:49.849
o'z-o'zini tiklashning yangi 
siklini boshlash

00:03:49.849 --> 00:03:51.279
uchun yana
uyquga ketadi.

00:03:51.689 --> 00:03:52.709
Mazkur metod har

00:03:52.709 --> 00:03:54.349
jihatdan tadqiq
etilganiga qaramay,

00:03:54.349 --> 00:03:55.689
uni ommaviy beton ishlab

00:03:55.689 --> 00:03:56.869
chiqarish jarayoniga

00:03:56.869 --> 00:03:58.909
joriy qilinishiga shoshmaslik zarur.

00:03:58.963 --> 00:04:01.503
Nima bo'lganda ham bu sporalar 
betonni yanada